  "logNo": "220665152967",
  "title": "이수한의원의 크리스마스 이브",
  "addDate": "2016. 3. 25.",
  "categoryNo": "43",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=220665152967",
  "html_size": 187085,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220665152967\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220665152967\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">2015년 크리스마스 때 올려야할 글을 못올리고 있었네요 ㅠㅠ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그때 컴퓨터 바이러스때문에 인터넷 이용하는게 너무 조심스러워서</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">못올렸었는데..</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">3개월이나 지났지만..&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그래도 지금이라도 올립니다 ㅎㅎ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">자...</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">2015년 12월 24일의&nbsp;이수한의원으로&nbsp;돌아갑니다~</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오늘은 크리스마스 이브 2015년 12월 24일, 이수한의원입니다 </p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">내일은 크리스마스</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">이수한의원에 오시는 단골 손님께서 치료받으러 내원하시면서</span></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">크리스마스 선물을 사오셨어요</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">종이 가방 두개를 주셨는데..</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">짠~</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160325_280/isuhani_1458891791939xzeJP_JPEG/PC245028.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160325_280/isuhani_1458891791939xzeJP_JPEG/PC245028.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003360AB05C7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160325_280/isuhani_1458891791939xzeJP_JPEG/PC245028.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">뭐가 들었는지 궁굼하시죠?</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6d7e671d61ddeee8.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"568\" style=\"cursor: pointer; line-height: 1.5; rheight: 568px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160325_133/isuhani_1458891815398ORGEt_JPEG/PC245029.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003360AB05C7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6d7e671d61ddeee8.jpg\"></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160325_150/isuhani_1458891816208pSCvP_JPEG/PC245030.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; line-height: 1.5; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160325_150/isuhani_1458891816208pSCvP_JPEG/PC245030.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003360AB05C7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160325_150/isuhani_1458891816208pSCvP_JPEG/PC245030.JPG?type=w3\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">가방 한개에는.. 음.. 초코 푸딩!^^</span></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">초코 색깔이 참 맛있게 생겼죠?</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">실제로도 엄청 달고 맛있답니다</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">잘먹었습니다 #꾸벅</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">우리 환자분의 마음처럼 참 스윗(SWEET)했답니다 ㅎㅎ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">이수한의원이 샤방샤방~</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5620e74e2b561a5e.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160325_157/isuhani_1458891841800dNfBk_JPEG/PC245031.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003360AB05C7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5620e74e2b561a5e.jpg\">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">다른 가방 하나는 원장님선물인데..</span></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">사진 찍는다고 몰래 꺼내봤어요 ㅠㅠ</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">보온병 같은데.. 열어보진 않아서 잘은 모르겠는데 </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">우리 원장님 이번 겨울에 따뜻하게 보내시라고 사주신거 같아요</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">선물 감사합니다~</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">환자분도 재밌고 추억에 남는 즐거운 크리스마스를 보내셨으면 좋겠습니다</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">모두 2015년은 잘 마무리 하시고, 2016년에는 행복하고 좋은일들만 가득하길 바래요~</span></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">건강하세요</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">... 라고 진작에 올렸어야는데 ㅠ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a9e77285bc15d1be.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-29\"></a>&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
